Daniels Igoni, Yenagoa Bayelsa State governor-elect, David Lyon, has constituted a 59-member transition committee of the All Progressives Congress. The names of the APC transition committee members were contained in a statement by the state party chairman, Jothan Amos, on Thursday. According to the statement, the committee is chaired by a former acting governor and Speaker of the state House of Assembly, Werinipre Seibarugu; while a former Head of Service, Obegha Oworibo, will serve as secretary. The APC transition committee is expected to work together with the state governmentâ€™s 41-member transition committee inaugurated by Governor Seriake Dickson on November 19. Copyright PUNCH.
